    "This exploration aims to extract additional insights, contributing to a more nuanced understanding of AI governance and enriching the discourse on enhance the ethical and responsible use of artificial intelligence (AI).• Ethical and Responsible AI Governance: In this study, Ethical and responsible AI governance represents a foundational set of values, and guidelines intended to guide the development, deployment, and utilization of artificial intelligence technologies in a manner that aligns with societal, moral, and legal considerations.",
